field.name: Military Family
field.sifPath: The field is determined based on existence of the participated by the student during the survey period FL-PGM-MFS program. If the participations exist, return 'Y', otherwise default value 'N' is used. If grade level of the student on the survey period start date is PK, returned value is 'Z'.

field.name: Grade Level
Year Entered 9 Grade
field.sifPath: If grade level of the student on the survey period snapshot date is '09', '10', '11', '12',the field is determined based on concatenation of value from [all-std-NinthGradeYear] + the value incremented by 1.

field.name: Resident Status
field.sifPath: The value from [all-enr-ResidentStatus] of enrollment with 'enrEnrType' equal to 'E' and that is the most recent on or before the survey period snapshot date.
